 ED nurse/ED physician; Objects: history)"><bpmn:incoming>Flow_29</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:outgoing>Flow_30</bpmn:outgoing></bpmn:task><bpmn:task id="activity6" name="assess and document fluid balance (Role: ED nurse; Objects: intake/output, vitals)"><bpmn:incoming>Flow_30</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:outgoing>Flow_31</bpmn:outgoing></bpmn:task><bpmn:task id="activity7" name="assess and document pressure sore risk (Role: ED nurse; Objects: pressure sore risk tool/skin assessment)"><bpmn:incoming>Flow_31</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:outgoing>Flow_32</bpmn:outgoing></bpmn:task><bpmn:task id="activity8" name="assess and document hydration and nutrition (Role: ED nurse/dietitian; Objects: hydration status, nutrition status)"><bpmn:incoming>Flow_32</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:outgoing>Flow_33</bpmn:outgoing></bpmn:task><bpmn:task id="activity9" name="assess and document pain (Role: ED nurse/ED physician; Objects: pain score, analgesia response)"><bpmn:incoming>Flow_33</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:outgoing>Flow_34</bpmn:outgoing></bpmn:task><bpmn:task id="activity10" name="assess and document temperature (Role: ED nurse; Objects: temperature reading)"><bpmn:incoming>Flow_34</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:outgoing>Flow_35</bpmn:outgoing></bpmn:task><bpmn:task id="activity11" name="assess and document other collateral injuries (Role: ED physician; Objects: secondary survey findings)"><bpmn:incoming>Flow_35</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:outgoing>Flow_36</bpmn:outgoing></bpmn:task><bpmn:task id="activity12" name="assess and document comorbid conditions (Role: ED physician; Objects: medical history/problem list)"><bpmn:incoming>Flow_36</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:outgoing>Flow_37</bpmn:outgoing></bpmn:task><bpmn:task id="activity13" name="assess and document current drug therapy including any anticoagulants (Role: ED physician/ED pharmacist; Objects: medication history, anticoagulant details)"><bpmn:incoming>Flow_37</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:outgoing>Flow_38</bpmn:outgoing></bpmn:task><bpmn:task id="activity14" name="assess and document continence (Role: ED nurse; Objects: continence status)"><bpmn:incoming>Flow_38</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:outgoing>Flow_39</bpmn:outgoing></bpmn:task><bpmn:task id="activity15" name="assess and document pre-fracture functional ability and mobility (Role: ED physiotherapist/ED nurse; Objects: baseline mobility/ADL history)"><bpmn:incoming>Flow_39</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:outgoing>Flow_40</bpmn:outgoing></bpmn:task><bpmn:task id="activity16" name="assess and document physical and functional level (Role: ED physiotherapist/ED physician; Objects: functional assessment findings)"><bpmn:incoming>Flow_40</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:outgoing>Flow_41</bpmn:outgoing></bpmn:task><bpmn:task id="activity17" name="assess and document mental state based on pre-morbid functioning using validated screening tool (MMSE, MOCA, or CAM) (Role: ED clinician; Objects: MMSE/MOCA/CAM result, collateral history)"><bpmn:incoming>Flow_41</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:outgoing>Flow_42</bpmn:outgoing></bpmn:task><bpmn:task id="activity18" name="assess and document social circumstances including caregiver status, community supports, and family involvement (Role: ED social worker/ED nurse; Objects: social history, caregiver/support details)"><bpmn:incoming>Flow_42</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:outgoing>Flow_56</bpmn:outgoing></bpmn:task><bpmn:task id="dummy_Flow_43" name="(dummy branch entry)"><bpmn:outgoing>Flow_48</bpmn:outgoing><bpmn:incoming>Flow_54</bpmn:incoming></bpmn:task><bpmn:exclusiveGateway id="exclusivegateway2" name="Exclusive Gateway"><bpmn:outgoing>Flow_44</bpmn:outgoing><bpmn:outgoing>Flow_46</bpmn:outgoing><bpmn:incoming>Flow_48</bpmn:incoming></bpmn:exclusiveGateway><bpmn:task id="activity19_2" name="order standard hip fracture lab panel plus anticoagulation/coagulopathy tests (Role: ED physician; Objects: CBC, electrolytes, renal function, glucose, coagulation studies, type&amp;screen/crossmatch as per policy)"><bpmn:incoming>Flow_44</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:outgoing>Flow_45</bpmn:outgoing></bpmn:task><bpmn:task id="act